These Cookies are persistent but time-limited cookies. These Cookies contain a
unique key to distinguish individual users’ browsing habits. We also use these
Cookies to limit the number of times a user sees a particular ad on a website
and to measure the effectiveness of a particular campaign. The identifier
stored by these Cookies are provided by our partners. We cannot use the same
identifier in our own systems.
